                  </persName> was indicted<rs id="t18440205-677-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18440205-677-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18440205-677-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp> for stealing 1 habit-shirt and collar, value 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18440205-name-898" type="victimName">
